{
  "id": "63536c978b1ed0002059098e",
  "title": "平仄",
  "created": 1666411675,
  "updated": 1666428991,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63536c978b1ed0002059098e",
      "text": "平仄",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666411675,
      "updated": 1666411675
    },
    {
      "id": "63536c9a5e90c00000b9106d",
      "text": "ひょうそく",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666411675,
      "updated": 1666411678
    },
    {
      "id": "63536cc45e90c00000b91071",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666411717,
      "updated": 1666411717
    },
    {
      "id": "63536c9d5e90c00000b9106f",
      "text": "[漢詩]、特に[近体詩]で使われているルールらしいのだがよく知らない[yits-khawk'9483.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666411678,
      "updated": 1666411719
    },
    {
      "id": "63536cbb5e90c00000b91070",
      "text": " なので調べよう",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666411707,
      "updated": 1666411712
    },
    {
      "id": "63536c9d5e90c00000b9106e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666411678,
      "updated": 1666411678
    },
    {
      "id": "63536cde5e90c00000b91072",
      "text": "中国語に[声調]がある",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666411742,
      "updated": 1666411758
    },
    {
      "id": "63536d125e90c00000b91078",
      "text": " 南斉の[沈約]らが「四声八病説」を定めて広まる",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666411794,
      "updated": 1666411860
    },
    {
      "id": "63536ced5e90c00000b91074",
      "text": "  [平声]（ひょうしょう。平らな音）",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666411758,
      "updated": 1666411918
    },
    {
      "id": "63536d085e90c00000b91075",
      "text": "  [上声]（じょうしょう。下から上がる音）",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666411785,
      "updated": 1666411921
    },
    {
      "id": "63536d095e90c00000b91076",
      "text": "  [去声]（きょしょう。上から落ちる音）",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666411786,
      "updated": 1666411923
    },
    {
      "id": "63536d0b5e90c00000b91077",
      "text": "  [入声]（にゅうしょう/にっしょう。語尾が詰まる音）",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666411787,
      "updated": 1666411925
    },
    {
      "id": "63536e615e90c00000b9107e",
      "text": "  「八病」はやってはいけない内容のこと",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666412130,
      "updated": 1666412150
    },
    {
      "id": "63536e765e90c00000b9107f",
      "text": "   [https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/四声八病説#:~:text=%E3%80%8C八病説%E3%80%8Dは%E3%80%81,紐%E3%80%8Dの名称がある%E3%80%82 四声八病説 - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666412150,
      "updated": 1666412156
    },
    {
      "id": "63536ce35e90c00000b91073",
      "text": "\t声。これって[詩吟]の話？ではない？[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1666411747,
      "updated": 1666411945
    },
    {
      "id": "63536dc8b8bbfc0000851b0a",
      "text": "\t\tそもそも言語には[声調]という概念があるのか",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1666411977,
      "updated": 1666412082
    },
    {
      "id": "63536e32b8bbfc0000851b0b",
      "text": "\t\t\t≒[トーン]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1666412083,
      "updated": 1666412111
    },
    {
      "id": "63536e3a5e90c00000b9107d",
      "text": "   [アクセント]の問題かも[yits-khawk'9483.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666412090,
      "updated": 1666412112
    },
    {
      "id": "63536d8fb8bbfc0000851b09",
      "text": "  詩吟にも関係していそう[yits-khawk'9483.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666411920,
      "updated": 1666412014
    },
    {
      "id": "63536db75e90c00000b9107b",
      "text": "   平仄自体は漢詩を制作するときのルールで文章上の話ではある",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666411959,
      "updated": 1666412063
    },
    {
      "id": "63536dbc5e90c00000b9107c",
      "text": "   でも[朗詠]することもあるので、実際に吟ずる方にも影響してるかも",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666411964,
      "updated": 1666412063
    },
    {
      "id": "63536eb65e90c00000b9108a",
      "text": " 最初は細かい配列規定があったようだが、「平」と「仄」の二種類に分けて配列するようになった",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666412214,
      "updated": 1666412297
    },
    {
      "id": "63536fce5e90c00000b91093",
      "text": "   唐代の発音で判断するらしい",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666412495,
      "updated": 1666412495
    },
    {
      "id": "63536f095e90c00000b9108b",
      "text": "  平声：平声",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666412297,
      "updated": 1666413068
    },
    {
      "id": "63536f145e90c00000b9108c",
      "text": "  仄声：上声、去声、入声",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666412309,
      "updated": 1666413073
    },
    {
      "id": "63536dac5e90c00000b91079",
      "text": " ならべかた",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666411948,
      "updated": 1666412679
    },
    {
      "id": "635370875e90c00000b9109b",
      "text": "  起句の二字目が平声か仄声かで判断する",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666412679,
      "updated": 1666413078
    },
    {
      "id": "635371e65e90c00000b910a2",
      "text": "   ×：自由、○：平声、●：仄声、◎：押韻（同じ韻を持つ漢字にする）",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666413030,
      "updated": 1666413135
    },
    {
      "id": "635370d85e90c00000b9109c",
      "text": "  平起式",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666412760,
      "updated": 1666412777
    },
    {
      "id": "635370f25e90c00000b9109d",
      "text": "   table:平起式(七言絶句)",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666412786,
      "updated": 1666412966
    },
    {
      "id": "635370fa5e90c00000b9109e",
      "text": "    起句\t×○\t×●\t●○◎",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666412966,
      "updated": 1666412977
    },
    {
      "id": "635371015e90c00000b9109f",
      "text": "    承句\t×●\t×○\t×●◎",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666412966,
      "updated": 1666412998
    },
    {
      "id": "635371135e90c00000b910a0",
      "text": "    転句\t×●\t×○\t×●●",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666412966,
      "updated": 1666413016
    },
    {
      "id": "635371185e90c00000b910a1",
      "text": "    結句\t×○\t×●\t●○◎",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666412966,
      "updated": 1666413023
    },
    {
      "id": "63536fbe5e90c00000b91090",
      "text": "  仄起式",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666412478,
      "updated": 1666412785
    },
    {
      "id": "63536fb55e90c00000b9108f",
      "text": "   table:平起式(七言絶句)",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666412469,
      "updated": 1666413150
    },
    {
      "id": "6353725e5e90c00000b910a3",
      "text": "    起句\t×●\t×○\t×●◎",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666413150,
      "updated": 1666413201
    },
    {
      "id": "6353725e5e90c00000b910a4",
      "text": "    承句\t×○\t×●\t●○◎",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666413150,
      "updated": 1666413208
    },
    {
      "id": "6353725e5e90c00000b910a5",
      "text": "    転句\t×○\t×●\t×○●",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666413150,
      "updated": 1666413215
    },
    {
      "id": "6353725e5e90c00000b910a6",
      "text": "    結句\t×●\t×○\t×●◎",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666413150,
      "updated": 1666413222
    },
    {
      "id": "635372ba5e90c00000b910aa",
      "text": "  実際の例",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666413242,
      "updated": 1666413245
    },
    {
      "id": "6353732c5e90c00000b910af",
      "text": "   [https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/少年老いやすく学なりがたし 少年老いやすく学なりがたし - Wikipedia]は「平起式」",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666413356,
      "updated": 1666414369
    },
    {
      "id": "6353af945e90c00000f52f78",
      "text": "    下の「発音」は[新選漢和辞典]の四声より",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666428820,
      "updated": 1666428991
    },
    {
      "id": "635372bd5e90c00000b910ab",
      "text": "   >少年易老學難成",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666413245,
      "updated": 1666413366
    },
    {
      "id": "635373fa5e90c00000b910b3",
      "text": "    table:初句",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666413562,
      "updated": 1666413576
    },
    {
      "id": "635373635e90c00000b910b1",
      "text": "    \t文字\t少\t年\t易\t老\t學\t難\t成",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666413411,
      "updated": 1666413604
    },
    {
      "id": "635374135e90c00000b910b4",
      "text": "    \t平仄\t●\t○\t●\t●\t●\t○\t◎",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666413587,
      "updated": 1666413606
    },
    {
      "id": "6353741d5e90c00000b910b5",
      "text": "    \t発音\tshào\tnián\tyì\tlǎo\txué\tnán\tchéng",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666413598,
      "updated": 1666413727
    },
    {
      "id": "635373295e90c00000b910ac",
      "text": "   >一寸光陰不可輕",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666413353,
      "updated": 1666413367
    },
    {
      "id": "635374a35e90c00000b910b6",
      "text": "   \ttable:承句",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666413731,
      "updated": 1666413789
    },
    {
      "id": "635374ab5e90c00000b910b7",
      "text": "    \t文字\t一\t寸\t光\t陰\t不\t可\t輕",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666413739,
      "updated": 1666413756
    },
    {
      "id": "635374ab5e90c00000b910b8",
      "text": "    \t平仄\t●\t●\t○\t○\t●\t●\t◎",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666413739,
      "updated": 1666413951
    },
    {
      "id": "635374ab5e90c00000b910b9",
      "text": "    \t発音\tyī\tcùn\tguāng\tyīn\tbù\tkě\tqīng",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666413739,
      "updated": 1666413977
    },
    {
      "id": "635373295e90c00000b910ad",
      "text": "   >未覺池塘春草夢",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666413353,
      "updated": 1666413368
    },
    {
      "id": "635375a45e90c00000b910ba",
      "text": "   \ttable:転句",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666413988,
      "updated": 1666414019
    },
    {
      "id": "635375ac5e90c00000b910bb",
      "text": "    \t文字\t未\t覺\t池\t塘\t春\t草\t夢",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666413996,
      "updated": 1666414012
    },
    {
      "id": "635375ac5e90c00000b910bc",
      "text": "    \t平仄\t●\t●\t○\t○\t○\t●\t●",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666413996,
      "updated": 1666414157
    },
    {
      "id": "635375ac5e90c00000b910bd",
      "text": "    \t発音\twèi\txué\tchí\ttáng\tchūn\tcǎo\tmèng",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666413996,
      "updated": 1666414152
    },
    {
      "id": "635373295e90c00000b910ae",
      "text": "   >階前梧葉已秋聲",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666413353,
      "updated": 1666413369
    },
    {
      "id": "63536dac5e90c00000b9107a",
      "text": "\t\t\t\ttable:転句",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666411948,
      "updated": 1666414175
    },
    {
      "id": "6353765e5e90c00000b910be",
      "text": "    \t文字\t階\t前\t梧\t葉\t已\t秋\t聲",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666414175,
      "updated": 1666414188
    },
    {
      "id": "6353765e5e90c00000b910bf",
      "text": "    \t平仄\t○\t○\t○\t●\t●\t○\t◎",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666414175,
      "updated": 1666414336
    },
    {
      "id": "6353765e5e90c00000b910c0",
      "text": "    \t発音\tjiē\tqián\twú\tyè\tyǐ\tqiū\tshēng",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1666414175,
      "updated": 1666414331
    },
